### Dashboard Statistics API Tests

### 1. Login as Admin
POST http://localhost:4000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@example.com",
  "password": "admin123"
}

### 2. Get Dashboard Stats
GET http://localhost:4000/api/dashboard/stats
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 3. Get Revenue Chart (7 days)
GET http://localhost:4000/api/dashboard/revenue?period=7days
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 4. Get Revenue Chart (30 days)
GET http://localhost:4000/api/dashboard/revenue?period=30days
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 5. Get Revenue Chart (12 months)
GET http://localhost:4000/api/dashboard/revenue?period=12months
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 6. Get Order Status Distribution
GET http://localhost:4000/api/dashboard/order-status
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 7. Get Recent Orders
GET http://localhost:4000/api/dashboard/recent-orders?limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 8. Get Best Selling Products
GET http://localhost:4000/api/dashboard/best-selling?limit=5
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
